Define the law and graph it
========================================================

Using base R

```{r, eval = FALSE}
BenfordsLaw <- function(d) log10(1 + 1 / d)
digits <- 1:9
baseBarplot <- barplot(BenfordsLaw(digits), 
    names.arg = digits, 
    xlab = "First Digit", ylim = c(0, .4),
    main = "Proportion of numbers with given First Digit")
```

